                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method and application of supported copper-chromium catalyst",
                    "一种负载型铜铬催化剂的制备方法及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of catalyst preparation and fine chemical engineering, and particularly relates to a preparation method of a supported copper-chromium bimetallic catalyst and application of the supported copper-chromium bimetallic catalyst in preparation of benzaldehyde through direct oxidation of methylbenzene. The preparation method of the supported copper-chromium bimetallic catalyst comprises the following steps: dissolving a nitrogen source, a carbon source, a copper source and a chromium source in water, then adjusting the pH value to 8-11, and then fully stirring; heating to evaporate moisture; calcining at the temperature of 300 to 800 DEG C for 2 to 8 hours; the supported copper-chromium bimetallic catalyst is obtained. The method for preparing benzaldehyde through direct oxidation of toluene comprises the following steps: dissolving toluene in a solvent, then adding the supported copper-chromium bimetallic catalyst and a hydrogen peroxide aqueous solution, heating to 40-95 DEG C, and carrying out a heat preservation reaction for 3-7 h in a stirring state to generate benzaldehyde. According to the method, expensive equipment is not needed, the production cost is low, the process is simple, the reaction conditions are mild, and the method has good industrial application potential."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于催化剂制备与精细化工领域，具体涉及一种负载型铜铬双金属催化剂的制备方法及其在甲苯直接氧化制苯甲醛中的应用。负载型铜铬双金属催化剂的制备方法为：将氮源、碳源、铜源、铬源溶解于水中，而后调节pH值为8～11，再充分搅拌；接着加热蒸发水分；再于300～800℃煅烧2～8h；得到负载型铜铬双金属催化剂。甲苯直接氧化制苯甲醛的方法为：将甲苯溶解在溶剂中，随后加入负载型铜铬双金属催化剂和过氧化氢水溶液，加热至40～95℃于搅拌状态下保温反应3～7h，生成苯甲醛。本发明不需要昂贵的设备、生产成本较低、工艺简单、反应条件温和，具有良好的工业化应用潜力。"
                }
            ]
